      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "### PSUDOCODE: Social Media Post Formatting Utility\n\nDEFINE FUNCTION GetValueFromMap(DataSource, SearchKey):\n    ITERATE through DataSource:\n        IF entry matches SearchKey:\n            RETURN associated value\n    RETURN NULL\n\nDEFINE FUNCTION FormatContent(RawString):\n    INITIALIZE CleanedString as RawString\n    INITIALIZE TargetURL as EMPTY\n\n    // HANDLE LINK EXTRACTION\n    IF RawString contains Markdown Link Syntax:\n        EXTRACT URL from parentheses\n        REPLACE Markdown syntax with the raw URL in CleanedString\n    ELSE IF RawString contains Plain URL:\n        EXTRACT URL as TargetURL\n        REMOVE metadata/formatting artifacts (e.g., \"smartCard\")\n\n    // DATA CLEANUP\n    REPLACE escaped characters (e.g., \"\\#\") with standard characters\n    TRIM whitespace from CleanedString\n\n    RETURN [CleanedString, TargetURL]\n\n// --- MAIN EXECUTION ---\nINITIALIZE OutputList as EMPTY\nFETCH InputItems from Source\n\nFOR EACH Item in InputItems:\n    EXTRACT Description and CategoryID\n    \n    // PROCESS DATA\n    SET [FinalCaption, FinalURL] = CALL FormatContent(Description)\n    SET CategoryName = CALL GetValueFromMap(CategoryList, CategoryID)\n\n    // CONSTRUCT OUTPUT\n    CREATE Object with { FinalCaption, FinalURL, CategoryName }\n    ADD Object to OutputList\n\nRETURN OutputList"
      },
